snippet.title: The Black Rose | Trailer
snippet.description:
The Black Rose is a student project developed during 7 weeks at Future Games
http://futuregames.se/

Download now for FREE:
https://unallocated.itch.io/the-black-rose

Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/TheBlackRoseGame/

Developers:
Alfred Ruckle - Game Design, Programming
John Walden - Game Design, Music & Sound Design
Malin Wong - Game Design, Level Design
Lovisa Pärli - 2D, Art Lead
Lilly Wang - 2D
Sabina Byström - 3D
Vincent Brandt - 3D, Technical Artist
Corinne Boman - 3D
Stephanie Strand - 3D, Animations
Marcus Björk - Programming
Dag Wirström - Programming
Khomsan Bangbor - Programming

Extra credits:
Emanuel Axelsson - Voice Acting
